block content

  div(class="container-featured container-featured-with-bg text-center")
    div(class="container")

      div(class="row")
          div(class="row")
            div(class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2")
              div(class="box")
                h2(class="text-red text-center") We take your happiness seriously
                br
                p(class="text-black description") That's why when you pre-order Lauren Zander's honest, funny, and in-your-face book, Maybe It's You, you'll also get Inner.U, our digital coaching course, at half-price!
                p(class="text-red description no-margin-bottom") We dare you to care about yourself as much as we do.
                br
                h4(class="text-black no-margin-bottom")
                  a(href="http://www.hachettebookgroup.com/titles/lauren-handel-zander/maybe-its-you/9780316318662/", class="link-lg js-track", data-track="btn-preorder-receipt") Pre-order the book
